                <head>463. Editorial Note</head>
                <p>In conjunction with the Syrian crisis, on August 28 the United States expedited
                    delivery to Iraq of certain items included in the Military Assistance Program.
                    Documentation concerning the deliveries is in Department of State, Central File
                    787.56. Regarding the Syrian crisis, see <ref target="frus1955-57v13#pg_617"
                        >volume XIII, pages 617</ref> ff.</p>
            </div>
